00:02:34.630 --> 00:02:35.630
Boredom.

00:02:35.630 --> 00:02:37.630
Also known as tedium monotony.

00:02:37.630 --> 00:02:39.630
Nothing to do.

00:02:39.630 --> 00:02:41.630
When your life just seems to go on

00:02:41.630 --> 00:02:43.630
