00:02:43.630 --> 00:02:45.630
Same old school.

00:02:45.630 --> 00:02:46.630
Same old friends.

00:02:46.630 --> 00:02:47.630
Same old room.

00:02:47.630 --> 00:02:49.630
Same old me.

00:02:49.630 --> 00:02:52.630
Now, if I lived somewhere else,

00:02:52.630 --> 00:02:53.630
someplace exotic,

00:02:53.630 --> 00:02:54.630
someplace exciting,

00:02:54.630 --> 00:02:56.630
someplace different,

00:02:56.630 --> 00:02:58.630
I'd never be bored.

00:02:58.630 --> 00:03:05.920
