00:03:22.920 --> 00:03:34.730
So, Father, what should we do this afternoon?

00:03:34.730 --> 00:03:36.730
Well, we could continue meditating.

00:03:36.730 --> 00:03:39.730
Oh, we've been meditating since last Thursday.

00:03:39.730 --> 00:03:42.730
