00:03:56.930 --> 00:03:59.930
Well, we could be rude to the tourists.

00:03:59.930 --> 00:04:01.930
Alert, not again.

00:04:01.930 --> 00:04:10.570
Well, there's always the Jerry-Louis Film Fest.

00:04:10.570 --> 00:04:12.570
Okay, forget Paris.

00:04:12.570 --> 00:04:14.570
Looks like Omwe's a universal phenomenon.

00:04:14.570 --> 00:04:16.570
I read somewhere that the longer you board,

00:04:16.570 --> 00:04:19.570
the better the chances you'll become really boring yourself.

00:04:19.570 --> 00:04:21.570
It's kind of the chicken and the egg thing.

00:04:21.570 --> 00:04:23.570
Well, whichever came first,

00:04:23.570 --> 00:04:25.570
I better do something fast.

00:04:25.570 --> 00:05:19.830
Or boredom becomes a way of life.

00:05:19.830 --> 00:05:21.830
I think it was Betty Crocker who said,

00:05:21.830 --> 00:05:23.830
those who can, do.

00:05:23.830 --> 00:05:25.830
Those who are bored, bake.

00:05:25.830 --> 00:05:28.830
The world's first right-side-up, upside-down cake.

00:05:28.830 --> 00:05:31.830
Well, this should kill another 15 minutes.

00:05:31.830 --> 00:05:33.830
I was so bored today, I started off the morning

00:05:33.830 --> 00:05:36.830
