00:05:43.830 --> 00:05:45.830
Maybe something I can wear around the house.

00:05:45.830 --> 00:05:49.240
All around the house.

00:05:49.240 --> 00:05:51.240
Knit one, pearl of gazillion.

00:05:51.240 --> 00:05:53.240
Is this what they mean by knit wit?

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:55.240
Seems like one meaningless activity

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:59.990
