00:05:59.990 --> 00:06:04.650
Ah, the domino effect.

00:06:04.650 --> 00:06:07.650
I guess it was exciting while it lasted.

00:06:07.650 --> 00:06:09.650
About three seconds.

00:06:09.650 --> 00:06:12.650
And now, this cake.

00:06:12.650 --> 00:06:14.650
Is there anything more boring than boredom?

00:06:14.650 --> 00:06:16.650
Oh, yeah.

00:06:16.650 --> 00:06:19.650
Ah, is this your entry for the Big Loser Bake Off?

00:06:19.650 --> 00:06:21.650
No, I'm looking at it.

00:06:22.650 --> 00:06:25.650
Well, I hope we got some of the things she likes to eat.

00:06:25.650 --> 00:06:27.650
What were you talking about?

00:06:27.650 --> 00:06:29.650
We're having a visitor, Sport.

00:06:29.650 --> 00:06:30.650
In an album?

00:06:30.650 --> 00:06:32.650
No, you remember Cokie Henderson?

00:06:32.650 --> 00:06:34.650
