00:06:34.650 --> 00:06:35.650
My old college roommate.

00:06:35.650 --> 00:06:36.650
Oh, yeah.

00:06:36.650 --> 00:06:38.650
She's coming to visit?

00:06:38.650 --> 00:06:39.650
No, but her daughter is.

00:06:39.650 --> 00:06:41.650
Piper will be with us for a whole week.

00:06:41.650 --> 00:06:43.650
Cool, but why would she want to come here?

00:06:43.650 --> 00:06:45.650
She's checking out colleges.

00:06:45.650 --> 00:06:47.650
She's coming to look at our old alma mater.

00:06:47.650 --> 00:06:48.650
Yeah, Sport.

00:06:48.650 --> 00:06:50.650
You know, it'll be like having a sister for the week.

00:06:50.650 --> 00:06:52.650
And having one for your whole life.

00:06:52.650 --> 00:06:54.650
Oh, I think you're both going to really like her.

00:06:54.650 --> 00:06:56.650
Yeah, I think it'd be interesting to spend some time

00:06:56.650 --> 00:06:58.650
with somebody who grew up in New York City.

00:06:58.650 --> 00:07:00.650
Except for when they lived in London.

00:07:00.650 --> 00:07:01.650
Oh, that's right.

00:07:01.650 --> 00:07:02.650
Oh, in Istanbul.

00:07:02.650 --> 00:07:04.650
Well, won't you be bored here?

00:07:04.650 --> 00:07:06.650
Not if you stay in your room.

00:07:06.650 --> 00:07:07.650
There's nothing to do.

00:07:07.650 --> 00:07:09.650
I should know I've tried everything.

00:07:09.650 --> 00:07:11.650
Oh, I'm sure you'll find a way to have fun together

00:07:11.650 --> 00:07:12.650
and make her feel at home.

00:07:12.650 --> 00:07:14.650
Yeah, so I'm going to go set up the study for her.

00:07:14.650 --> 00:07:15.650
Great.

00:07:15.650 --> 00:07:18.090
I'll help you get it ready.

00:07:18.090 --> 00:07:19.090
Great.

00:07:19.090 --> 00:07:21.090
How am I going to entertain a total stranger

00:07:21.090 --> 00:07:22.090
