00:07:29.090 --> 00:07:30.090
sophisticated,

00:07:30.090 --> 00:07:31.090
in a word,

00:07:31.090 --> 00:07:32.090
moi.

00:07:32.090 --> 00:07:33.090
In a word, yuck.

00:07:33.090 --> 00:07:35.090
I understand the civic opera.

00:07:35.090 --> 00:07:37.090
I think our guests might enjoy

00:07:37.090 --> 00:07:41.680
box seats.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:42.680
Piper.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:43.680
Hmm.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:45.680
Finally someone new and different.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:47.680
Hey, nothing lasts forever.

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:48.680
Not even boredom.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:53.540
I guess I could put my World of Craft Kit away now.

00:07:53.540 --> 00:07:55.540
Piper is coming in the nick of time.

00:07:55.540 --> 00:07:57.540
I was just about to get started on those origami

00:07:57.540 --> 00:07:59.540
toothpick holders.

00:07:59.540 --> 00:08:02.540
But what are we going to do once Piper gets here?

00:08:02.540 --> 00:08:03.540
She's been everywhere.

00:08:03.540 --> 00:08:07.780
She'll probably have a ton of ideas.

00:08:07.780 --> 00:08:11.660
Hi, Sam.

00:08:11.660 --> 00:08:12.660
Not so loud.

00:08:12.660 --> 00:08:15.940
What's going on?

00:08:15.940 --> 00:08:16.940
