00:08:20.940 --> 00:08:23.940
She's all over me like a cheap sweatsuit.

00:08:23.940 --> 00:08:24.940
That's some crush.

00:08:24.940 --> 00:08:26.940
This is not a crush.

00:08:26.940 --> 00:08:30.940
Maria Teresa Koolbaum is like my own personal fan club.

00:08:30.940 --> 00:08:32.940
She's relentless.

00:08:32.940 --> 00:08:35.940
Wednesday she sent me flowers, Thursday candy,

00:08:35.940 --> 00:08:38.940
