00:08:38.940 --> 00:08:39.940
No.

00:08:39.940 --> 00:08:40.940
Yes.

00:08:40.940 --> 00:08:41.940
No.

00:08:41.940 --> 00:08:42.940
What's a passionogram?

00:08:42.940 --> 00:08:44.940
