00:08:49.940 --> 00:08:50.940
Wow.

00:08:50.940 --> 00:08:51.940
This is worse than serious.

00:08:51.940 --> 00:08:52.940
It's pathetic.

00:08:52.940 --> 00:08:54.940
Do you even like her a little?

00:08:54.940 --> 00:08:56.940
Well, she's nice and everything,

00:08:56.940 --> 00:08:59.940
but no, she's giving me the creeps.

00:08:59.940 --> 00:09:01.940
Sam, you've got to tell her you're just not interested.

00:09:01.940 --> 00:09:02.940
I did.

00:09:02.940 --> 00:09:05.940
But she told me that subconsciously I want to be chased.

00:09:05.940 --> 00:09:07.940
I feel like the fugitive,

00:09:07.940 --> 00:09:09.940
and I can't find the one-armed man.

00:09:09.940 --> 00:09:11.940
You mind if I hide out here for a while?

00:09:11.940 --> 00:09:12.940
No problem.

00:09:12.940 --> 00:09:14.940
I'm just getting ready for Piper to get here from New York.

00:09:14.940 --> 00:09:15.940
Hey, that's right.

00:09:15.940 --> 00:09:16.940
New York.

00:09:16.940 --> 00:09:19.940
Maybe she knows how to deal with psychopaths.

00:09:19.940 --> 00:09:20.940
And boredom.

00:09:20.940 --> 00:09:29.300
What are you doing, Ferguson?

00:09:29.300 --> 00:09:31.300
I'm just trying to make Piper feel a little more at home.

00:09:31.300 --> 00:09:33.300
Who's home, the Duchess of Dorkhead?

00:09:33.300 --> 00:09:35.300
You wouldn't understand.

00:09:35.300 --> 00:09:37.300
Sophisticated New Yorkers like Piper

00:09:37.300 --> 00:09:39.300
