00:09:39.300 --> 00:09:42.300
Tea sandwiches, classy music.

00:09:42.300 --> 00:09:43.300
Just the beginning.

00:09:43.300 --> 00:09:46.300
I think tomorrow we'll start with a continental breakfast,

00:09:46.300 --> 00:09:47.300
