00:10:37.090 --> 00:10:38.090
That's okay.

00:10:38.090 --> 00:10:40.090
I'll, uh, send her a postcard later.

00:10:40.090 --> 00:10:43.090
Oh, well, um, you must be tired.

00:10:43.090 --> 00:10:45.090
Whatever.

00:10:45.090 --> 00:10:46.090
You'll be staying in the study.

00:10:46.090 --> 00:10:47.090
Let's get you settled in.

00:10:47.090 --> 00:10:49.090
Thanks, whatever.

00:10:49.090 --> 00:10:51.090
Hey, after you unpack, Piper,

00:10:51.090 --> 00:10:52.090
