00:11:03.090 --> 00:11:07.320
Thanks.

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:11.320
So, hey, that's Piper, huh?

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:13.320
Great kid.

00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:19.110
You know, a little shy, maybe.

00:11:19.110 --> 00:11:24.110
Am I the only one who finds her just a tad disturbing?

00:11:24.110 --> 00:11:29.290
Well, she looks cool, I guess.

00:11:29.290 --> 00:11:32.290
It could be interesting hanging out with Piper.

00:11:32.290 --> 00:11:34.290
I guess.

00:11:34.290 --> 00:11:36.290
Yeah, it'll be fun.

00:11:36.290 --> 00:11:38.290
I guess.

00:11:38.290 --> 00:11:39.290
Oh, well.

00:11:39.290 --> 00:11:40.290
Whatever.

00:11:40.290 --> 00:11:47.860
I know, we can go rollerblading.

00:11:47.860 --> 00:11:49.860
Rollerblading?

00:11:49.860 --> 00:11:50.860
I don't think so.

00:11:50.860 --> 00:11:52.860
But, uh, don't let me keep you.

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:54.860
I'm just not into that stuff.

00:11:54.860 --> 00:11:57.860
Well, there's the battle of the bands down by the lake.

00:11:57.860 --> 00:11:58.860
Thanks, that's okay.

00:11:58.860 --> 00:12:01.860
Well, what would you like to do?

00:12:01.860 --> 00:12:03.860
I really don't mind doing nothing.

00:12:03.860 --> 00:12:04.860
This is fine.

00:12:04.860 --> 00:12:05.860
Really?

00:12:05.860 --> 00:12:07.860
Yeah, I said it isn't.

00:12:07.860 --> 00:12:08.860
Hanging out's great.

00:12:08.860 --> 00:12:10.860
It's, uh, comfortable.

00:12:10.860 --> 00:12:12.860
It's stress-free.

00:12:12.860 --> 00:12:15.860
Yep, no tension at all.

00:12:15.860 --> 00:12:22.120
So, what would you be doing if you were in New York?

00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:25.120
Probably going to the movies with my friends.

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.120
Movies?

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.120
We've got movies.

